pageContext.claim: “Can you believe that with all of the made up, unsourced stories I get from the Fake News Media, together with the  $10,000,000 Russian Witch Hunt (there is no Collusion), I now have my best Poll Numbers in a year. Much of the Media may be corrupt, but the People truly get it!”
pageContext.analysis: The investigation into possible links between the Trump campaign and Russian operatives continues, and no conclusions have been reached. There's no reason to believe it is a "witch hunt."
